--
-- VHDL Architecture Splitter.iisEncoder.inputLRCK
--
-- Created:
--          by - maxime.cesalli.UNKNOWN (WE2330804)
--          at - 08:46:24 02.06.2023
--
-- using Mentor Graphics HDL Designer(TM) 2019.2 (Build 5)
--
